|Che li approda~ = ^che pro gli fa~: "What good will
it do him?"
..TEXT:
|approda~ = ^fa pro~; cf. the Latin ^prodesse.~
As Malacoda advances toward Virgil, he addresses his comrades
behind him, or perhaps only himself.
